dd rustling sounds, somebody seemed to be continuously approaching from behind the bushes, the chill and the hardness of the stone slab hurt his bare knees; and Mary lay there too submissive, too still.

He stopped; then emitted an awkward short laugh. “I keep feeling that someone’s around,” said Ganin and got up.

Mary sighed, rearranged her dress—a whitish blur—and stood up, too.

